{"ID":"20260424101903-5m46v7o","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-5m46v7o","title":"10_综合案例","type":"doc","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-906uq9h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-906uq9h","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10 从模型到系统的闭环案例"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-p0zpb6j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-p0zpb6j","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前九卷已经把 NPU 设计拆成若干层：工作负载、计算核心、数据流、量化、编译器、runtime、系统约束、平台案例。最后这一卷的任务不是再加新知识，而是把这些层重新串起来，证明它们在真实工程里是一条连续链，而不是十个独立专题。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-3rmctcn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-3rmctcn","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里选一个足够典型、又不会被细节噪声淹没的案例："}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-ilgp1e1","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-ilgp1e1","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260424101903-9x5e0rn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-9x5e0rn","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在边缘端做一个小型图像分类模型推理，目标是单帧低延迟、低功耗、可持续运行，并且软件栈能够稳定部署。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-j9ehgn3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-j9ehgn3","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这个案例不是为了代表所有模型，而是为了说明："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"从工作负载到系统落地，每一层设计如何互相约束"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-68i7kdj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-68i7kdj","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 先把问题定义清楚"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-h63euz7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-h63euz7","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"假设目标场景如下："}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-k6t49he","Type":"NodeLis