e","TextMarkTextContent":"fully-int8 TFLite + edgetpu_compiler"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，不满足约束的层可能留在 CPU；若走 OpenVINO NPU 一类平台，关键则变成 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"compile_model(\"NPU\") + model cache + driver/plugin/compiler"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 的闭环，以及 static-shape 等平台边界。也就是说，综合案例里的“编译成功”必须具体到平台语境，不能只写成泛泛的 codegen 成功。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-3rsb460","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-3rsb460","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8. Runtime 和驱动如何把一次推理跑通"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-0ireimw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-0ireimw","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译器产物准备好以后，runtime 和驱动的最小闭环大致是："}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-84c764j","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-84c764j","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-rrezjv8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-rrezjv8","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-5nr3vm9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-5nr3vm9","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"初始化 device / context / stream"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-h0br39l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-h0br39l","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-k9y1n5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-k9y1n5c","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"装载模型工件"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-s3ti907","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-s3ti907","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-tm89i1p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903