{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"tile、局部缓存、双缓冲、DMA 重叠"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"带宽和片上容量是否够"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数值优化"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"INT8 + 融合 + 局部高精度保留"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据路径是否整体变轻"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译器"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"融合、映射、memory plan、codegen"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"runtime 能否稳定装载和执行"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"runtime/驱动"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上下文、缓冲区、命令提交、同步"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"端到端性能和稳定性是否成立"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"系统约束"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"功耗、热、安全、扩展边界"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是否需要改到多核或不同平台"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-r44v7s2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-r44v7s2","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果这七步里任何一层和上下层脱节，系统就会出现一种典型症状："}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-incxacn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-incxacn","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-y19batc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-y19batc","updated":"20260